Review Updated Label Translations
We updated the translations for some standard object, tab, and field names for these languages: Chinese (Simplified), Danish, Dutch, Finnish, German, Greek, Hungarian, Japanese, Spanish, Spanish (Mexico), Norwegian, Russian, Slovenian, and Turkish.

This change applies to Lightning Experience, Salesforce Classic, and all versions of the mobile app in all editions. 
To review the changes, see Review Summer ‘24 Updated Label Translations and download the attached list.
